{"analysis_markdown_path":"articles/2026/06/07/itm_25cdea8ffbbe90fd/index.md","canonical_url":"https://arxiv.org/abs/2606.02373","category_id":"llm-agent","collected_at":"2026-06-06T23:41:31Z","content_hash":"9d668f87c44e92daeac16bddef2e200eb774c9d8aa9c4505ade4b9d4bba5e28b","evidence":[{"label":"arXiv abstract","type":"url","url":"https://arxiv.org/abs/2606.02373"},{"label":"arXiv PDF","type":"url","url":"https://arxiv.org/pdf/2606.02373"},{"label":"GitHub repository","type":"url","url":"https://github.com/pat-jj/harness-1"},{"label":"Hugging Face model","type":"url","url":"https://huggingface.co/pat-jj/harness-1"}],"external_id":"arxiv:2606.02373","fetched_at":"2026-06-06T23:41:31Z","fingerprint":"9d668f87c44e92daeac16bddef2e200eb774c9d8aa9c4505ade4b9d4bba5e28b","id":"itm_25cdea8ffbbe90fd","item_id":"itm_25cdea8ffbbe90fd","language":"zh-CN","published_at":"2026-06-01T15:21:41Z","reading_minutes":28,"score":94,"sort_at":"2026-06-01T15:21:41Z","source_id":"arxiv","source_name":"arXiv","source_type":"manual","summary_zh":"Harness-1 是一个基于 gpt-oss-20b 的 20B 搜索子 Agent，把候选池、curated set、重要性标签、全文库、证据图、验证记录、去重压缩和预算控制外置到 stateful harness，policy 只学习搜索、阅读、精选、验证和停止等语义动作。论文用 GPT-5.4 teacher 生成并过滤 899 条 SFT 轨迹，再在 SEC 的 3,453 个 query 上用 on-policy CISPO RL 训练约 82K rollout；8 个检索 benchmark 上平均 curated recall 达 0.730，比下一强 open search subagent 高 11.4 点，held-out transfer 平均增益 17.0 点。局限是完整复现依赖 BrowseComp+ 数据、Chroma collection、OpenAI/可选 Baseten 检索栈和 CUDA/vLLM 环境，证据图也仍是 regex 级抽取。","tags":["LLM Agent","Search Agent","Reinforcement Learning","Harness","Evidence Retrieval"],"title":"Harness-1: Reinforcement Learning for Search Agents with State-Externalizing Harnesses","title_hash":"f4e0b3f642d9b7363b8ad5f403ec5fe587f43143803bbe1d60c1fc872dde74dc","type":"paper","updated_at":"2026-06-01T15:21:41Z","url":"https://arxiv.org/abs/2606.02373"}
